<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>Your Tickets</title>
  <style>
    * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
    body { font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; background: #f4f4f4; }
    .container { max-width: 700px; margin: 0 auto; background: #fff; box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.1); }
    .header { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #4CAF50 0%, #45a049 100%); color: white; padding: 30px; text-align: center; }
    .content { padding: 40px 30px; }
    .ticket-list { margin: 20px 0; }
    .ticket-card { background: #f8f9fa; border-radius: 12px; padding: 20px; margin: 20px 0; border: 2px dashed #28a745; }
    .ticket-header { text-align: center; margin-bottom: 15px; }
    .event-name { font-size: 20px; font-weight: bold; color: #28a745; margin-bottom: 5px; }
    .detail-row { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; padding: 8px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid #e9ecef; }
    .detail-row:last-child { border-bottom: none; font-weight: bold; color: #28a745; }
    .important-note { background: #fff3cd; border-left: 4px solid #ffc107; padding: 15px; margin: 20px 0; }
    .footer { background: #f8f9fa; padding: 20px 30px; text-align: center; color: #6c757d; font-size: 14px; }
    @media (max-width: 600px) { .container { margin: 0 10px; } .content, .header { padding: 20px 15px; } }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>🎟️ Your Tickets Are Ready!</h1>
      <p>Attached are all your tickets for {{eventName}}</p>
    </div>

    <div class="content">
      <h2>Hello {{userName}},</h2>
      <p>Thank you for your purchase! You’ve booked <strong>{{ticketCount}}</strong> tickets for <strong>{{eventName}}</strong>.  
      All tickets are included in the attached PDF. Here’s a summary:</p>

      <div class="ticket-list">
        {{#each tickets}}
          <div class="ticket-card">
            <div class="ticket-header">
              <div class="event-name">{{eventName}}</div>
              <p style="color:#6c757d;">Ticket ID: {{ticketId}}</p>
            </div>
            <div class="detail-row">
              <span>📅 Date:</span>
              <span>{{formatDate eventDate}}</span>
            </div>
            <div class="detail-row">
              <span>📍 Venue:</span>
              <span>{{venue}}</span>
            </div>
            <div class="detail-row">
              <span>🎫 Type:</span>
              <span>{{ticketType}}</span>
            </div>
            {{#if seatNumber}}
            <div class="detail-row">
              <span>💺 Seat:</span>
              <span>{{seatNumber}}</span>
            </div>
            {{/if}}
            <div class="detail-row">
              <span>💰 Price:</span>
              <span>{{formatCurrency price}}</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        {{/each}}
      </div>

      <div class="important-note">
        <h4>⚠️ Important Information:</h4>
        <ul style="margin-left: 20px; margin-top: 10px;">
          <li>Your full tickets are attached as a PDF.</li>
          <li>Please arrive at least 30 minutes before the event starts.</li>
          <li>Each ticket contains a unique QR code — do not share them.</li>
          <li>Bring a valid ID for verification if required.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <p>We’re excited to see you at <strong>{{eventName}}</strong>! 🎉</p>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
      <p>&copy; 2025 EventHub. All rights reserved.</p>
      <p>Need help? Contact us at <a href="mailto:support@eventhub.com">support@eventhub.com</a></p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
